{
  "stem": "1282.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he would perform.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He would cut the throat and test the lungs, blow up the lungs, see for any damages.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because in the Jewish tradition, if you pull the lungs out, and especially from a geese, and there are lungs are spattered, they're trayf.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There's a little humorous story to this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My father-- I was always the-- among the three boys, I was considered to be the most religious one and destined to be a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my father always told me, he says, son, when you go to the shochet and he performs the test, one thing never do.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Never ask, is it kosher?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He may say no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But if you don't ask, and you come home, and he didn't say anything, it's kosher.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was a tradition at that time, and when you have three sons-- and this goes back long, long in the bible-- where one son gets the inheritance of the family.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the other son becomes a tradesman, a professional man or a tradesman.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the third son studies Torah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it's the responsibility of those two sons to support the third son.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "While my father was not that religious that he would follow that tradition, but more or less, he did choose one son who would carry on the religious tradition, or possibly become a rabbi or whatever.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This was a wish or dream.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the one that was destined to be that, it's me because my oldest brother was very bright, very intelligent.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "At 13, he was speaking English, self-taught.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My second brother was very handy, [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Tibor, ?] or Ted, who is alive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He was very handy with his hands.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He made a fine mechanic He was destined to be the mechanic, or the professional.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
